<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" style="" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Dear {!Contact.Salutation} {!Contact.FirstName} {!Contact.LastName},</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">We are pleased to announce that we are now able to provide every parent with a personal login to the Parent Portal. Up to now we have only been able to provide one per family.</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">This change may effect your ability to log in to the&nbsp;Parent Portal&nbsp;for a few hours on&nbsp;Saturday 26th April. If you should find yourself unable to log in please be patient and wait for an email from us providing you with your new login information.</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">In the unlikely event that you are still unable to log in on Sunday 27th April and have not received an email with your login information then please contact us by sending an email to&nbsp;<a href="mailto: support@britishschools.co.uk">support@britishschools.co.uk</a>.</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">We apologise for any inconvenience this may cause but trust that you will enjoy having your own login in the future.</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Kind regards,</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Parent Portal<font style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;Support Team</font></font></div></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><div style="text-align: left;"><div style="text-align: left;"><div style=""><font style="" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></div></div></div></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><br></div>]]></td>
